1
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:29,370
=Fights Break Sphere=

2
00:01:40,290 --> 00:01:42,760
=Episode 6=

3
00:02:06,390 --> 00:02:07,880
What's the matter?

4
00:02:08,780 --> 00:02:13,400
I only found out today
that you are Gu Wenxin's child.

5
00:02:14,370 --> 00:02:17,030
If it wasn't for your mother's betrayal that year,

6
00:02:17,030 --> 00:02:21,380
how would it be possible for my parents
to die in the Extreme North area?

7
00:02:21,380 --> 00:02:24,030
How can you still have the face to live?

8
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:27,080
My mother is not a traitor.

9
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:28,740
Why should I believe you?

10
00:02:28,740 --> 00:02:32,440
If you don't believe me, kill me then.

11
00:02:32,440 --> 00:02:34,010
Do you think I don't dare to?

12
00:02:41,810 --> 00:02:44,640
If my mother is a traitor,

13
00:02:44,640 --> 00:02:48,300
why would she make the long trip home
for her death?

14
00:02:48,300 --> 00:02:53,150
I'm still alive right now
because I want to seek revenge for her.

15
00:02:55,140 --> 00:02:57,220
Everybody knows

16
00:02:57,220 --> 00:03:00,030
that Gu Wenxin conspired with Soul Hall

17
00:03:00,030 --> 00:03:02,510
and betrayed the sect.

18
00:03:03,990 --> 00:03:08,210
This will be the last time
you'll ever say those words to me.

19
00:03:08,210 --> 00:03:12,230
If you say them again,
even if you don't kill me,

20
00:03:12,230 --> 00:03:14,380
I will kill you.

21
00:03:16,710 --> 00:03:18,750
Is what you said all true?

22
00:03:20,460 --> 00:03:23,130
Go to sleep.
You need to restore your strength.

23
00:03:38,730 --> 00:03:39,830
Back off.

24
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:48,860
Xiao Yan! Come!

25
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:57,850
Attack me from behind.

26
00:04:09,260 --> 00:04:12,470
Xiao Yan, are you a piece of trash?

27
00:04:12,470 --> 00:04:14,540
You are a piece of trash!

28
00:04:14,540 --> 00:04:16,550
So, you just have this little bit of ability?

29
00:04:17,400 --> 00:04:19,330
After training today, I'm punishing you

30
00:04:19,330 --> 00:04:22,500
by making you clean up the training studio!

31
00:04:37,020 --> 00:04:38,550
Are you all right?

32
00:04:41,180 --> 00:04:42,830
I'm all right.

33
00:05:51,330 --> 00:05:53,510
You've been coming here more often lately.

34
00:05:56,110 --> 00:05:58,660
That Ge Ye, he uses his hidden energy every time.

35
00:05:58,660 --> 00:06:00,390
He beats me up until my whole body hurts.

36
00:06:00,390 --> 00:06:02,820
Even when it's time to sleep,
I'm afraid to lay down on the bed.

37
00:06:02,820 --> 00:06:04,950
If it wasn't for my Fight Qi protecting me,

38
00:06:04,950 --> 00:06:07,320
I would have possibly become a vegetable by now.

39
00:06:08,670 --> 00:06:11,800
Ge Ye is a part of the Nalan Clan.
Nalan Jie doesn't like you.

40
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:14,680
Ge Ye naturally wants to fawn over him.

41
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:16,620
The Nalan family.

42
00:06:18,380 --> 00:06:19,930
Wait till the day I've mastered the skills...

43
00:06:19,930 --> 00:06:22,390
So what. Even if you master the skills,

44
00:06:22,390 --> 00:06:24,540
it's not up to you to pick a fight.

45
00:06:25,340 --> 00:06:26,690
That's not true.

46
00:06:26,690 --> 00:06:30,690
Remember to thank those
that hurt and took advantage of you.

47
00:06:30,690 --> 00:06:33,910
If it wasn't for them,
you wouldn't be this persistent in pursuing progress.

48
00:06:33,910 --> 00:06:36,580
Come over here.
I'll teach you some new moves.

49
00:06:56,110 --> 00:06:57,670
Rapid Fire.

50
00:07:15,690 --> 00:07:17,370
Extract the medicine.

51
00:07:23,420 --> 00:07:25,020
What are you looking for?

52
00:07:25,020 --> 00:07:27,600
Looking for a spoon.

53
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:31,670
Do you think this is a beginner's class?
Use your hand to extract it.

54
00:07:40,740 --> 00:07:42,770
You must be really dumb.

55
00:07:42,770 --> 00:07:45,230
I told you to use your hands, which means
using your Fight Qi Skills to extract it.

56
00:07:45,230 --> 00:07:46,980
Do you have an indestructible body?

57
00:07:46,980 --> 00:07:49,230
How could you just insert your hand in there?

58
00:08:01,300 --> 00:08:02,680
How do I use my Fight Qi Skills to extract it?

59
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:05,480
Leave then. What are you back here for?

60
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:08,760
I won't fawn over you.

61
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:11,950
Go back to being the Young Master. Leave.

62
00:08:13,190 --> 00:08:14,870
Feel better?

63
00:08:15,500 --> 00:08:17,560
If you feel better now, hurry up and teach me.

64
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:20,930
My hand has already become some form of pig trotter paste.
How could you even have the nerve?

65
00:08:20,930 --> 00:08:22,710
Look closely.

66
00:08:27,850 --> 00:08:31,140
To truly extract the real Spiritual Solution of an herb,

67
00:08:31,140 --> 00:08:34,450
remember, the medicinal ingredients
mustn't fall into the cauldron.

68
00:08:34,450 --> 00:08:38,010
If the heat is too high, the purity
of the Spiritual Solution won't be enough.

69
00:08:40,450 --> 00:08:43,870
The critical point is to
turn your Fight Qi into a Fight Qi Whirl.

70
00:08:43,870 --> 00:08:46,270
This Fight Qi Whirl can be small or large,

71
00:08:46,270 --> 00:08:48,900
but it must be small enough
that you can subtly control it to

72
00:08:48,900 --> 00:08:51,400
let the medicine heat up evenly.

73
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:53,630
Once you're done extracting the Spiritual Solution,

74
00:08:54,620 --> 00:08:59,480
use your Qi Whirl to transfer it to a container.

75
00:09:02,560 --> 00:09:07,030
This requires sufficient Fight Qi and precise control.

76
00:09:07,030 --> 00:09:10,740
Just use your little pig trotter
to slowly understand it.

77
00:09:38,390 --> 00:09:41,730
Not bad. You've improved.

78
00:09:41,730 --> 00:09:43,400
My gratitude to Elder Ge for making that possible.

79
00:09:49,020 --> 00:09:51,570
Aren't you capable of blocking?

80
00:09:52,330 --> 00:09:53,990
You still have not done enough manual work.

81
00:09:53,990 --> 00:09:56,660
Today, you will continue your punishment
by doing manual work.

82
00:09:57,730 --> 00:09:59,510
Xiao Yan.

83
00:10:03,300 --> 00:10:06,090
Are you all right?

84
00:10:11,020 --> 00:10:14,000
It's fine for you to offend anyone,
but you just had to offend Elder Ge Ye.

85
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:16,430
Isn't that too reckless?

86
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:20,140
He is especially petty.

87
00:10:20,140 --> 00:10:23,750
The first years couldn't be quick enough
to fawn over him. Look at you.

88
00:10:23,750 --> 00:10:26,220
The main thing is I didn't offend him.

89
00:10:27,110 --> 00:10:30,600
No, if he punched you once,
you could have just laid down.

90
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:32,740
You even endured it.

91
00:10:32,740 --> 00:10:34,910
Are you trying to show off?

92
00:10:35,620 --> 00:10:38,900
Listen to your brother here. Don't do anything
that will show off your ability.

93
00:10:38,900 --> 00:10:41,080
The one who can swim drowns to death. The one who retorts
is beaten to death. [T/N: One should know one's limitations.]

94
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:43,360
Why do you want to set yourself up against him?

95
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:45,730
If you want to practice your skills,
go and rent a practice stage.

96
00:10:45,730 --> 00:10:48,710
No matter how you want to train, no one will care.

97
00:10:49,510 --> 00:10:50,510
Yes, you're right.

98
00:10:52,220 --> 00:10:56,390
It's this one here. This small building,
clean every room properly.

99
00:10:56,390 --> 00:10:58,280
This is the place where the teachers
practice their martial arts skills.

100
00:10:58,280 --> 00:11:02,390
They're eating at this moment.
Just work hard. Hurry, go.

101
00:11:02,390 --> 00:11:04,740
- Thank you.
- It's fine. Go...

102
00:11:50,250 --> 00:11:54,420
Brat, you dare to steal things here?

103
00:11:59,020 --> 00:12:01,270
You have some guts, don't you?

104
00:12:01,270 --> 00:12:02,690
I'm here to clean the washroom.

105
00:12:02,690 --> 00:12:05,980
This is Elder Gu He's medicine room.
Not just anyone is allowed to enter.

106
00:12:05,980 --> 00:12:07,540
Let's go. Go to the Elders' compound.

107
00:12:07,540 --> 00:12:09,170
Let's go. Let's go.

108
00:12:11,370 --> 00:12:14,430
Do you dare to hit me? Hit me once then.

109
00:12:15,260 --> 00:12:19,140
It's fine to go to the Elders' compound,
but I'm not a thief.

110
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:24,070
While we were on duty today,

111
00:12:24,070 --> 00:12:26,600
we passed by Elder Gu He's medicine room.

112
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:29,010
We heard a sound. This brat's unlucky.

113
00:12:29,010 --> 00:12:31,060
We caught him before he could steal.

114
00:12:31,060 --> 00:12:33,510
What do you mean "before I could steal?"

115
00:12:33,980 --> 00:12:35,700
He still does not admit to it.

116
00:12:40,990 --> 00:12:42,970
Obviously, Elder Ge Ye informed Bai Cheng

117
00:12:42,970 --> 00:12:45,040
to tell me to go clean the medicine room.

118
00:12:45,040 --> 00:12:48,730
While I was cleaning a shelf, I suddenly found
some broken medicine pellets on the floor.

119
00:12:48,730 --> 00:12:51,770
I was still in a state of wonder when the two of them
suddenly rushed in to accuse me of being a thief.

120
00:12:51,770 --> 00:12:54,450
- You two were mistaken.
- No, we were not.

121
00:12:55,710 --> 00:12:59,040
When did I tell you
to go and clean the medicine room?

122
00:12:59,040 --> 00:13:01,350
I told you to go and clean the training studio!

123
00:13:01,350 --> 00:13:04,190
Moreover, you have cleaned the training studio
for more than once.

124
00:13:04,190 --> 00:13:07,170
Don't you know by now that I was the one
who personally told you each time?

125
00:13:07,170 --> 00:13:11,600
Why would I need Bai Cheng to tell you? Ridiculous!

126
00:13:12,810 --> 00:13:15,290
That isn't right. Call Bai Cheng to come here.
Where is Bai Cheng?!

127
00:13:15,290 --> 00:13:18,470
A moment ago, we sent someone to find him.
He's waiting at the door now.

128
00:13:18,470 --> 00:13:20,860
Bai Cheng! Come in!

129
00:13:20,860 --> 00:13:24,100
Greetings to Elder Gu, Elder Tengshan,
Teacher Ruo Lin, and Elder Ge.

130
00:13:24,100 --> 00:13:26,470
Good? What is good? Stop talking nonsense!

131
00:13:26,470 --> 00:13:28,440
Tell them.

132
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:33,570
Did I ask you to inform Xiao Yan
to go and clean the medicine room?

133
00:13:34,410 --> 00:13:35,430
No.

134
00:13:35,430 --> 00:13:36,760
What did you say?

135
00:13:36,760 --> 00:13:38,170
Indeed, I did not.

136
00:13:38,170 --> 00:13:43,600
Brother Xiao said that he wanted to
tour the academy, so I showed him around.

137
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:46,840
I even specifically told him
that he could go anywhere,

138
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:49,910
- except Elder Ge's medicine room since it's
a forbidden place in the academy. - Right.

139
00:13:49,910 --> 00:13:53,480
That's not just applicable to us students.
Even the elders who want to enter

140
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:55,690
must give advance notice.

141
00:13:55,690 --> 00:13:58,700
Junior, how could you do that?

142
00:13:59,880 --> 00:14:01,730
Say it again.

143
00:14:01,730 --> 00:14:04,780
While I was on the way here a moment ago,
I already heard that you stole Elder Gu's medicine.

144
00:14:04,780 --> 00:14:08,500
Junior, it's one thing to be good or bad
as we learn fighting techniques.

145
00:14:08,500 --> 00:14:10,990
Behaving with integrity is the most important aspect.

146
00:14:14,560 --> 00:14:16,250
Jerk, I...

147
00:14:16,250 --> 00:14:18,310
Enough! Enough!

148
00:14:18,310 --> 00:14:19,990
Drag him away!

149
00:14:19,990 --> 00:14:22,150
- Yes.
- Yes.

150
00:14:22,150 --> 00:14:23,870
Go! Hurry.

151
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:33,730
He is a thief indeed. Elder Gu,
it's not a big loss. Right?

152
00:14:33,730 --> 00:14:36,130
The problem is not about loss.

153
00:14:36,130 --> 00:14:38,320
It's about bad character.

154
00:14:39,630 --> 00:14:42,510
I could see that Xiao Yan was very angry.

155
00:14:42,510 --> 00:14:45,810
How could a thief who was caught red-handed
be so bold and confident in his conviction?

156
00:14:45,810 --> 00:14:47,820
It is better to investigate a little more clearly.

157
00:14:47,820 --> 00:14:50,050
There is nothing else to investigate.

158
00:14:50,050 --> 00:14:52,340
Did you not see a moment ago?

159
00:14:52,340 --> 00:14:54,550
In front of us, he dared to hit people.

160
00:14:54,550 --> 00:14:55,520
Right.

161
00:14:55,520 --> 00:14:57,460
- Ignoring the academy's rules.
- Ignoring the academy's rules.

162
00:14:57,460 --> 00:14:58,430
What impropriety that was!

163
00:14:58,430 --> 00:15:00,440
We must deal with the matter.

164
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:02,530
I wholeheartedly agree.

165
00:15:03,370 --> 00:15:05,320
Tell us. How will we deal with this matter?

166
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:10,000
Expulsion? Abolish his Fight Qi skills?
Kick him out of the academy?

167
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:11,900
Kick him out of the academy.

168
00:15:11,900 --> 00:15:15,360
- Let him return to work at that medicine shop.
- Yes.

169
00:15:15,360 --> 00:15:18,330
- If there is no objection then, just do it this way.
- All right!

170
00:15:18,330 --> 00:15:21,740
I have seen many strange happenings.

171
00:15:22,300 --> 00:15:27,290
But I have never seen anyone steal
while holding a broom and a cleaning rag.

172
00:15:31,070 --> 00:15:32,860
Have you ever seen it?

173
00:15:34,060 --> 00:15:37,860
When Xiao Yan was found,
his hand was still holding a cleaning rag.

174
00:15:37,860 --> 00:15:41,800
Do thieves nowadays use a cleaning rag to steal?

175
00:15:43,070 --> 00:15:46,620
He did steal something.

176
00:15:46,620 --> 00:15:49,500
How is it related to a cleaning rag?

177
00:15:49,500 --> 00:15:51,170
Elders.

178
00:15:52,050 --> 00:15:55,880
All of you want to abolish
a child's Fight Qi skills and expel him.

179
00:15:55,880 --> 00:15:58,000
That is a very simple matter.

180
00:15:58,000 --> 00:16:02,240
But this child's life will be ruined by our hands.

181
00:16:02,240 --> 00:16:06,160
We are teachers.
Shouldn't we be a little more prudent?

182
00:16:06,970 --> 00:16:11,650
Elders, if you insist on dealing with
the matter in this way, convince me first.

183
00:16:11,650 --> 00:16:15,080
Why did he hold on to a broom
and a cleaning rag to steal?

184
00:16:17,800 --> 00:16:19,670
I... I...

185
00:16:21,670 --> 00:16:24,880
I... How would I know?

186
00:16:24,880 --> 00:16:28,250
Indeed. Someone saw him stealing

187
00:16:28,250 --> 00:16:31,730
and he didn't run away.
Instead, he went to quarrel with them.

188
00:16:31,730 --> 00:16:34,540
Where in this world
can you find such a bold thief?

189
00:16:35,640 --> 00:16:37,830
- He beat others. You must have seen that, right?
- Right.

190
00:16:37,830 --> 00:16:39,850
- What should be done about that?
- What should be done about that?

191
00:16:39,850 --> 00:16:43,540
According to the academy's rules,
punish him by confinement.

192
00:16:44,640 --> 00:16:46,170
That is not a problem, right?

193
00:16:49,080 --> 00:16:51,070
Then, let's just do it that way.

194
00:16:56,240 --> 00:16:59,260
- Obediently stay here.
- Let's go.

195
00:17:12,730 --> 00:17:14,560
What should we do?

196
00:17:16,339 --> 00:17:18,199
I am worried to death.

197
00:17:21,440 --> 00:17:23,970
Bai Cheng. Bai Cheng. Bai Cheng.

198
00:17:27,130 --> 00:17:28,930
What should we do?

199
00:17:28,930 --> 00:17:32,109
- What is the matter? - You're back.
- Why is Xiao Yan in confinement?

200
00:17:32,109 --> 00:17:34,939
All because of that jerk Bai Cheng
scheming with the Black White Evil Duo

201
00:17:34,940 --> 00:17:38,030
to slander Xiao Yan.
They said he stole Elder Gu's things.

202
00:17:38,030 --> 00:17:41,480
- Black White Evil Duo? They are black and white jerks!
- Right. Jerks.

203
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:45,940
Then, does Xun'er know about it yet?

204
00:17:45,940 --> 00:17:50,070
Xun'er was crying a while ago.
She's currently bringing a meal to Xiao Yan.

205
00:17:51,910 --> 00:17:53,330
- Hey!
- Move aside.

206
00:17:53,330 --> 00:17:54,430
- What are you doing?
- What are you doing?

207
00:17:54,430 --> 00:17:56,210
What are you doing? Let me tell you.

208
00:17:56,210 --> 00:17:58,770
It's not like you don't know
the Academy forbids private fighting.

209
00:17:58,770 --> 00:18:00,320
If you go there, what should we do?

210
00:18:00,320 --> 00:18:02,740
You are a coward. Move aside!

211
00:18:03,270 --> 00:18:04,910
Stay back.

212
00:18:04,910 --> 00:18:06,760
It is not that we are not helping.

213
00:18:06,760 --> 00:18:09,190
We must think of a way, right?

214
00:18:09,190 --> 00:18:14,100
That Black White Evil Duo has many men and great power.
If we just rush in, isn't that just seeking death?

215
00:18:14,110 --> 00:18:16,440
- RIght.
- Then, tell us what we should do?

216
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:22,570
Both of you take your time to think about it, all right?

217
00:18:23,900 --> 00:18:25,700
- Come back here.
- Don't go.

218
00:18:25,700 --> 00:18:27,870
What are you doing? Come back here!

219
00:18:27,870 --> 00:18:30,130
Hu Jia, you--

220
00:18:30,130 --> 00:18:34,400
Juniors, I heard your boss has been locked up.

221
00:18:40,470 --> 00:18:42,300
You... What do you want to do?

222
00:18:42,300 --> 00:18:44,320
What do I want to do?

223
00:19:25,400 --> 00:19:27,080
Everyone's here, right?

224
00:19:28,070 --> 00:19:30,970
No matter what happens tonight,

225
00:19:30,970 --> 00:19:33,130
everyone must keep it to yourselves.

226
00:19:33,130 --> 00:19:36,760
Whoever tends to talk in your sleep.
Cut off your tongue.

227
00:19:39,670 --> 00:19:41,550
Has the Master of Soul Hall arrived?

228
00:19:41,550 --> 00:19:43,410
Yes. Let us go.

229
00:20:20,700 --> 00:20:23,350
Brother Xiao Yan, we are here to get you.

230
00:20:27,230 --> 00:20:28,940
Let us go back then.

231
00:20:44,730 --> 00:20:47,030
[Thief]

232
00:20:59,630 --> 00:21:03,660
I forgot to tidy up.
Hu Jia and I will tidy up now.

233
00:21:08,420 --> 00:21:10,070
How many days have I been locked up?

234
00:21:10,070 --> 00:21:11,870
Three days.

235
00:21:13,770 --> 00:21:16,270
You all have suffered a lot, right?

236
00:21:16,270 --> 00:21:17,960
It was fine. What could have happened?

237
00:21:31,100 --> 00:21:33,240
All of you continue tidying up then.
I am going to sleep.

238
00:22:22,070 --> 00:22:23,900
That place seems to be a problem.

239
00:22:38,360 --> 00:22:40,020
Are they people from Soul Hall?

240
00:22:40,020 --> 00:22:42,890
The Blood Sect. The slaves of Soul Hall.

241
00:22:42,890 --> 00:22:44,770
- The Blood Sect?
- Yes.

242
00:22:45,630 --> 00:22:47,390
But there's something weird.

243
00:22:47,390 --> 00:22:50,280
Why would the Blood Sect infiltrate Jia Nan Academy?

244
00:22:50,280 --> 00:22:53,650
They even pulled aside several tens of students
to secretly meet with in there.

245
